{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On rainy days he, he didn't even ask us to-- he was counting us inside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other, his deputy, was named [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Meyer. ?] He, he was-- what rank would that be?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not officer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The highest rank before officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sergeant Major.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very, very rough and shouting at every one of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now that, that [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bush ?] really, he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think some, some people witnessed after liberation, put some good words in for him, whether it helped him, [INAUDIBLE], or not.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not for [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Meyer. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17 In December.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in Allach just, just four days before liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Still working in Allach in different little places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole 1,000 men all under [INAUDIBLE] organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still working with my father in the same group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just go back to where I was sidetracked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When, when I had so much raw potatoes, what to do with it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the German engineer from [INAUDIBLE] asked me to get a shovel and build him a one-man bunker against air raids.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because night time he, he could jump out from his little room, from his hot bed a couple meters away, and into that hole.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were fox holes, sort of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I started digging and it was still not too cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No one frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were a lot of roots there because it was bush setting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I build a sink and the [INAUDIBLE] the engineers held me to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We put four, four, four by two or four by four timbers in the four corners and a corrugated roof with some soil on it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he could have a vision, sloping slightly, and he had a vision all around open about two foot.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
